OL,3,CPaul Brand investigates how criminals
OL,4,Care exploiting the UK's waste system.
OL,6,FBritain is being blighted by rubbish,
OL,7,Flevels of fly tipping are now at
OL,8,Frecord highs. With the country facing
OL,9,Fan estimated #1 billion clean up bill,
OL,10,FPaul Brand has been looking at the
OL,11,Fscale of the issue and finding out who
OL,12,Firesponsible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
