PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778810610
OL,3,CPaul Brand investigates how criminals
OL,4,Care exploiting the UK's waste system.
OL,6,F'We had vermin in our house. In summer
OL,7,Flast year, the smells were so
OL,8,Funbearable that we couldn't cope. It
OL,9,Fgives you major anxiety of what it's
OL,10,Fgoing to cause in the future. We don't
OL,11,Fknow if it's affecting our health.'
OL,12,FThe site in Wigan has since been
OL,13,Fclosed and tipping has stopped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
