OL,3,CPaul Brand investigates how criminals
OL,4,Care exploiting the UK's waste system.
OL,6,FAt Kidlington in Oxfordshire an
OL,7,Festimated 20,000 tonnes of rubbish
OL,8,Fwere dumped on a site close to the
OL,9,FRiver Cherwell and a clearance cost of
OL,10,F#8 million to the tax payer, the site
OL,11,Fis currently under investigation by
OL,12,Fthe Environment Agency. When it comes
OL,13,Fto these large scale sites, the
OL,14,Fauthorities are stepping in, but on
OL,15,Fprivate land it's a different story.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
