OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778810610
OL,3,CPaul Brand investigates how criminals
OL,4,Care exploiting the UK's waste system.
OL,6,FTonight met with farmer Will in
OL,7,FHertfordshire whose neighbour's land
OL,8,Fhad been targeted by fly tippers. It's
OL,9,Fthought around 200 tonnes of toxic
OL,10,Fwaste were dumped on the land, but as
OL,11,Fit's on private land the farmer was
OL,12,Fleft to foot the bill for cleanup.
OL,13,FThey were quoted upwards of #60,000 to
OL,14,Fremove the waste, but thankfully good
OL,15,Fsamaritans stepped in and set up a
OL,16,Ffundraiser to help cover the cost of
OL,17,Fcleanup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
