PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778810610
OL,3,CPaul Brand investigates how criminals
OL,4,Care exploiting the UK's waste system.
OL,6,FThe government's newly launched Waste
OL,7,FCrime Action Plan hopes to combat this
OL,8,Fnationwide problem; the Environment
OL,9,FSecretary told the programme: "We've
OL,10,Fdoubled the enforcement budget of the
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency to put more boots
OL,12,Fon the ground to boost their
OL,13,Fcapability to crack down on these
OL,14,Fcriminals, and also to prevent these
OL,15,Fwaste dumps from happening in the
OL,16,Ffirst place." And the Environment
OL,17,FAgency hopes to seize funds from those
OL,18,Fresponsible to help foot the bill,
OL,19,Fmaking the criminals pay.
OL,21,FUseful Resource
